---
description: Environment variables reference for this project
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

Core:
- DATABASE_URL
- NODE_ENV (development|production)
- ANALYZE (true to enable bundle analyzer)

Site/Intl:
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL
- NEXT_PUBLIC_LOCALE_DETECTION (true|false)

Auth (Better Auth):
- NEXT_PUBLIC_BETTER_AUTH_URL
- BETTER_AUTH_SECRET
- NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID
- GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET
- NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID
- GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET
- TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY
- NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY

Stripe:
- STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
- STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
- STRIPE_CUSTOMER_PORTAL_URL (path, e.g. dashboard/subscription)

Creem:
- CREEM_API_KEY
- CREEM_WEBHOOK_SECRET
- CREEM_API_BASE_URL (optional, defaults to https://api.creem.io/v1)

Cloudflare R2:
- R2_ACCOUNT_ID
- R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID
- R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
- R2_BUCKET_NAME
- R2_PUBLIC_URL

Emails (Resend):
- RESEND_API_KEY
- ADMIN_EMAIL

AI Providers:
- OPENAI_API_KEY
- ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
- GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY
- DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
- XAI_API_KEY
- OPENROUTER_API_KEY
- REPLICATE_API_TOKEN
- NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_MODEL_ID (UI)
- NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_PROVIDER (UI)

Analytics/Tracking (optional):
- NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ID=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ADSENSE_ID=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_CLARITY_PROJECT_ID=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_PLAUSIBLE_SRC=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=
- PLAUSIBLE_API_KEY=
- PLAUSIBLE_URL=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_SRC=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_RYBBIT_SRC=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_RYBBIT_SITE_ID=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_RYBBIT_SESSION_REPLAY="true"
- NEXT_PUBLIC_RYBBIT_REPLAY_MASK_SELECTORS='[".user-name", "#email"]'
- NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=
- NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=

Pricing/Marketing:
- NEXT_PUBLIC_PRICING_PATH (e.g. pricing)
- NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_CURRENCY (e.g. usd)
- NEXT_PUBLIC_DISCORD_INVITE_URL

Images:
- NEXT_PUBLIC_OPTIMIZED_IMAGES (false to disable next/image optimization)
